                    "시간 절삭 $\\psi(t)u$의 푸리에 변환: $\\widetilde{\\psi u}(\\tau, \\xi) = \\hat{\\psi}(\\tau - \\xi^2) \\hat{u}_0(\\xi)$.",
                    "$X^{s,b}$ 노름 계산: $\\|\\psi u\\|_{X^{s,b}}^2 = \\int \\langle \\xi \\rangle^{2s} |\\hat{u}_0(\\xi)|^2 \\int |\\hat{\\psi}(\\sigma)|^2 \\langle \\sigma \\rangle^{2b}\\,d\\sigma\\,d\\xi$.",
